```
(Where feature is cyan, bug is red, P0 is red bold, open is green, etc.)

### Ready Command (with color)
```
Ready to work (5 issues):

[P0] beads_rust-abc123  Fix critical security bug          (alice)
[P1] beads_rust-def456  Implement login page               (unassigned)
```

